# Protocol & Database

- Every persisted entity carries `protocolVersion: 1`.
- Config JSON in SQLite must pass kind-specific Zod schema before insert.
- Use parameterized queries (`runAsync('... WHERE id = ?', id)`). Never interpolate user input.
- Schema changes: add migration step in `db/migrations.ts`, bump `CURRENT_SCHEMA_VERSION`.
- Export/import uses `ProtocolBundle` — same shape for backup and future sync.
